# User-dropped SillyTavern cards (keep bundled cards, license + .gitkeep);
# world books live INSIDE cards as the embedded character_book
cards/*
!cards/.gitkeep
!cards/LICENSE-CC-BY-SA-3.0.md
!cards/LunaMoth.zh.json
!cards/LunaMoth.en.json
!cards/Quinn.zh.json
!cards/Quinn.en.json
!cards/SCP-079.zh.json
!cards/SCP-079.en.json

# LunaMoth runtime artifacts
